{"tid":474171,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2013年 中華基督教會 基真小學女生墮樓慘劇","createTime":"2017-11-20T02:05:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T08:25:51.000Z","uid":44562,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"1db66fdb9036ab09565836082208ae314f11e97d","tid":474171,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:05:10.000Z","msg":"詳情 :<br />\n<a href=\"http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/2013%E5%B9%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%9C%9F%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E6%85%98%E5%8A%87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fevchk.wikia.com%2Fwiki%2F2013%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259F%25BA%25E7%259C%259F%25E5%25B0%258F%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E6%25A8%2593%25E6%2585%2598%25E5%258A%2587&d=Q%2FzATyi%2BLt4M8DTUOBGFiXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=ba485644\" target=\"_blank\">http://evchk.wikia.com/wiki/2013%E5%B9%B4%E5%9F%BA%E7%9C%9F%E5%B0%8F%E5%AD%B8%E5%A5%B3%E7%94%9F%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E6%85%98%E5%8A%87</a><br />\n<br />\n死者疑受校園欺凌<br />\n校方事後一直堅稱無收到死者受欺凌報告。惟死者的同學連日來紛在facebook留言悼念，並轉載一張有關校園欺凌的圖片，說明為「欺凌造成的傷害是一輩子的，如果你也反對欺凌，請分享！」其中有女同學更留言：「其實我好唔開心，你做乜咁睇唔開？我同你都算熟，我見過你比人蝦，我做乜唔幫？！好後悔，你好善良，知唔知？」不過，當記者追問詳情時，該同學卻三緘其口，聲稱並不認識墜樓女童：「不關我事的，我們已經很傷心。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裁定死因存疑<br />\n2015年7月24日，死因庭為此案作出裁決，指經考慮後無法裁定死者死於自殺或意外，最終裁定羅死因存疑。裁判官怒斥該校副校長石玲及高婉華均非誠實可靠證人，石的證供一派胡言，謊話連篇，石曾供稱死者當時在地上「好乾淨，好似瞓著咁」，說法令人難以置信。副校長高婉華曾於救護員到場時，向對方稱不須用擔架，死者可以行走的說法匪夷所思，裁判官認為她的說法只有兩個可能，分別為她真的不知道死者由高處墮下，或她想淡化事件。<br />\n<br />\n網民認為裁決大致公平，並怒斥相關教職員在庭上的種種說法無恥冷血。<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3c/11046878_10153636466917448_8559651025716281442_n.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/400?cb=20150724055100\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3c%2F11046878_10153636466917448_8559651025716281442_n.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F400%3Fcb%3D20150724055100&h=ed075e28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2e2ab9ea29801dbe557ccbf0e73d838e3d8063b","tid":474171,"uid":25556,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"教畜禍港"},{"pid":"985ee6e8da9b2d735d9c9b5c71cc8988656d0a94","tid":474171,"uid":108467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T02:23:14.000Z","msg":"好似仲只係叫St John救護車，冇報警/叫消防處救護車"},{"pid":"1db4c89fffd8f1fca8b23e1bd473300dba3c88ca","tid":474171,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7822043fb609a3a625db6da970d3243963e03cf","tid":474171,"uid":143241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T03:11:44.000Z","msg":"以前喺舊登都已經話佢係畀人掉落樓"},{"pid":"aeedac17125db4caee41f31c32fcf946e6a4377c","tid":474171,"uid":121825,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:34:40.000Z","msg":"Btw 有無09年畢業校友？想揾番個英文老師 姓呂"},{"pid":"83bad22baf7ac59aedcf54425e84fb2700031918","tid":474171,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"4年後冇一個人需要負責 繼續出糧"},{"pid":"90376746675f340965cbfcc2b4fc424e8941bf55","tid":474171,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"一定要教畜仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833775616690e2df560970306e59915763609592","tid":474171,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:17:45.000Z","msg":"又係中華基督教會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cddafaf14bc256d8e1ecca5ec81cc293dd859e12","tid":474171,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前喺舊登都已經話佢係畀人掉落樓</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5aab39bdaa6b0c033f59a54b6fda9b349